# Keep the Docker build context small + correct. Without this, `COPY . .` drags
# the host node_modules (pnpm symlinks with absolute paths) and stale dist into
# the image, which bloats and can break the in-image `pnpm install` / build.
**/node_modules
**/dist
.git
.github
**/*.log
**/.turbo
**/coverage
.DS_Store
*.local
